reviewText: My mom loves all cantinflas movies, good quality

Great deal. I got this for my dad and he is happy with it. I would recommend this product to any Cantinflas fans out there.
Who does not love Cantinflas? I can watch them over and over and laugh like the first time! Also very cheap!!!
With Cantinflas you can never go wrong. Hilarious comedy.

I loved watching these movies as a kid growing up. Good, honest humor, and nothing vulgar about them. Cantinflas was the greatest comedian actor of his time, and all his movies had a lesson or 2 to teach. I can truly say, my quick wit to respond with sarcasm to people and my fast spoken humor... is because of this great Mexican actor's movies.
Its a real classic in very nice format. Good quality, good price!!
best quality movies, two in one!
Bought it for my father,he is 87, and he loves it and can't beat that price!
